metadata.name: CryptoMoss #S
metadata.description:
CryptoMoss #S

by @Vusiuz | Codename: Spectrum | 

A variant of glitchmoss that stuck on some multidimensional projections. It can phase around digital objects and also have an unstable state that makes it occasionally glitching.


Cryptomoss is Random Living Moss Species that grow over Cryptoworld, Each number is created because accidentally randomized simulations that even the creator, @vusiuz cant even replicate again :D
